Made an appointment for our 3 months old baby, waiting for the appointment for 2 weeks confirming it 2 times and they called us to cancel it when we were standing right in front of their door, because they take only adult patients.

Ridiculous customer service. Not recommended at all.

I've been going to Mi Doctor since they opened. The first doctor i've met was Dr.Polly He is the best. He's very attentive , He resolves my issues, I always leave his office feeling better and Ease.

I recommend this office to anybody who is feeling ill or needs a primary care doctor or need the covid test or for any small emergency.

originalText.text: I've been seeing Dr. Michelle Li for 10 years as my PCP and I always feel welcome, well-treated and encouraged.  This wellness visit was to determine if I have any maladies before setting off on an overseas trip.  Dr. Li made me very comfortable as did her staff.  Great physician.

originalText.text: My appt was terrific. The staff was so friendly & process of getting the appointment & wait time was terrific. I only gave the rating a 4 instead of a 5 bc they have the most up to date facility but not technician to operate the X-ray or ultrasound. Not their fault. MiDoctor needs to fill those positions. Hopefully soon.
